{"about_the_game":"Build Your Abilities<br>Destroy Your Enemies<br>Go As Far As You Can<br>Die<br>Repeat<br><br>In this <strong>roguelite arcade shooter</strong> you'll have to build your <strong>custom abilities</strong>. To create an ability you can chain up to four skills, each one will trigger the next one upon hitting an enemy. On top of that you'll be able to customise even more your abilities by adding effects to each skill of your chain. <br><br>You'll encounter waves <strong>procedurally generated enemies</strong> in <strong>procedurally generated maps</strong>, making each run unique, find the right build to explode them all. Each time you finish a map you'll be allowed to <strong>enhance your build</strong> before going to the next map and your next enemies. Take care of the <strong>elites</strong> and the <strong>bosses</strong> or they'll end your runs.<br><br>Each map will be <strong>bigger</strong> than the previous one, enemies will be <strong>harder</strong>, <strong>stronger</strong> and there'll be more of them, brace yourself.<br><br>Do your worst, try our <strong>challenges</strong>, put your name on the <strong>leaderboards</strong>, <strong>embrace the infinity</strong>.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Getting Started","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2164980/1ed1ba559c27bbcc1d9ca11c23c69b26303e81ab.jpg"},{"name":"Learning the Tropes","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2164980/a6dfa576188739d999028a5836f20f387d62b957.jpg"},{"name":"Who's the boss now?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2164980/b7e19c95ff1aa5bf30270c3f29eb03dd19fe7cc6.jpg"},{"name":"Serial killer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2164980/d151c03eced0fe076a25eac813711ba24ceae2a2.jpg"},{"name":"Elitist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2164980/7079c2f36d8fa5